### Uni Pilot API - Career Tree Tests
### Tests for fetching the career tree structure

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@apiVersion = v1

### Use token from login (optional for career tree - it's public)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Career Tree for Study Program (Public endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/study-programs/1/career-tree
Accept: application/json

### 2. Get Career Tree for Study Program ID 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/study-programs/2/career-tree
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get Career Tree - Different Study Program
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/study-programs/3/career-tree
Accept: application/json

### 4. Select Job (requires authentication)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/profile/job
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "job_id": 11
}

### 5. Select Job - Example: React Developer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/profile/job
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "job_id": 86
}

### 6. Select Job - Example: Backend Developer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/users/me/profile/job
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "job_id": 112
}

### 7. Generate Roadmap for Job (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/jobs/11/roadmap/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Generate Roadmap for React Developer Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/jobs/86/roadmap/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. Create Chat Session for Job (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/jobs/11/chat/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. Create Chat Session for React Developer Job
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/jobs/86/chat/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Send Message in Job Chat Session (requires authentication)
### First get session_id from step 9 or 10, then use it here
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/chat/sessions/1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

